%3ELarry%20Summers%20said%20on%20the%20All-In%20Podcast%20that%20DOGE%20is%20wreaking%20havoc%20on%20US%20institutions.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20pointed%20to%20the%20administration's%20targeting%20of%20the%20Internal%20Revenue%20System.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20former%20treasury%20secretary%20said%20the%20outcome%20could%20put%20the%20US%20into%20further%20debt.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFormer%20Treasury%20Secretary%20Larry%20Summers%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoge-department-of-government-efficiency%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDOGE%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20end%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bdisastrous%20failure%2C%26quot%3B%20possibly%20leading%20the%20US%20into%20a%20deeper%20deficit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESummers%20said%20on%20an%20episode%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKcmMOZKnKAk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAll-In%20Podcast%3C%2Fa%3E%20posted%20on%20Friday%20that%20he%20generally%20agrees%20that%20the%20US%20government%20could%20be%20more%20efficient.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20we%20need%20much%20more%20reform%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20agreeing%20with%20New%20York%20Times%20columnist%20Ezra%20Klein%2C%20another%20guest%20on%20the%20show.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20Democrats%20have%20allowed%20themselves%20excessively%20to%20become%20hostage%20to%20particular%20groups%2C%20particular%20traditional%20concerns%2C%20and%20have%20lost%20touch%20in%20important%20ways%20with%20the%20American%20mainstream.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESummers%20said%2C%20however%2C%20that%20the%20current%20administration%20and%20DOGE%20are%20wreaking%20havoc%20on%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffederal-agencies-musk-doge-targeted-list-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerican%20institutions%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20surmised%20that%20they%20would%20fail%20to%20solve%20the%20problems%20they're%20trying%20to%20address%2C%20such%20as%20the%20national%20deb