ess%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20arrived%20for%20the%20practice%20rounds%20at%20Augusta%20National%20this%20week%2C%20he%20had%20a%20small%20point-and-shoot%20camera%20in%20his%20pocket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20cellphone%2C%20however%2C%20was%20absent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222180%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Masters%20champion%20Scottie%20Scheffle%20attends%20the%20Masters%20in%20April%202025.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67fabd023fe8d3928362f0d5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221635%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EScottie%20Scheffler%20at%20the%202025%20Masters%20at%20Augusta%20National%20Golf%20Club.%3Cp%3EAugusta%20National%2FAugusta%20National%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAttendees%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmasters-rules-dos-donts-kicked-out-arrested-2018-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprohibited%20from%20bringing%20cellphones%3C%2Fa%3E%20onto%20Augusta%20National's%20grounds%20during%20the%20tournament.%20Other%20electronic%20items%2C%20like%20laptops%2C%20tablets%2C%20radios%2C%20and%20TVs%2C%20are%20also%20a%20no-go%20at%20the%20Masters.%20Patrons%20violating%20these%20policies%20could%20be%20removed%20from%20Augusta%20National's%20grounds%20and%20lose%20their%20tickets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20era%20of%20ubiquitous%20screens%20and%20nonstop%20notifications%2C%20the%20Masters%20keeps%20things%20analog.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20peaceful%2C%26quot%3B%20Wahlberg%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20like%20camping.%20You%20slowly%20detach.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAttending%20the%20Masters%20means%20disconnecting%20from%20the%20world%20for%20sometimes%20hours%20at%20a%20time%2C%20which%20can%20cause%20problems%20for%20people%20who%20rely%20on%20our%20super-connected%20society%20for%20work.%20A%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20reporter%20wrote%20that%20some%20working%20in%20finance%20who%20attended%20the%20tournament%20on%20Wednesday%20were%20unaware%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20that%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20announced%20a%2090-day%20pause%20on%20many%20tariffs%20until%20he%20told%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWahlberg%20felt%20a%20%26quot%3Bphantom%20buzzing%26quot%3B%20in%20his%20pocket%20for%20the%20first%20few%20hours%20at%20the%20Masters%20but%20said%20the%20lack%20of%20cellphones%20is%20part%20of%20the%20event's%20magic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20sit%20next%20to%20other%20patrons%2C%20and%20nobody%20has%20a%20face%20in%20a%20screen%2C%20so%20you're%20forced%20to%20have%20conversations%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20couldn't%20tell%20you%20the%20names%20of%20anybody%20we%20sat%20by%2C%20but%20I%20could%20rehash%20all%20the%20conversations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPatrons%20at%20the%20Masters%20aren't%20completely%20off%20the%20grid%2C%20though.%20Instead%2C%20they%20wait%20in%20line%20to%20use%20pay%20phones%20provided%20by%20the%20golf%20club.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225351%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Patrons%20attend%20the%20Masters%20at%20Augusta%20National%20Golf%20Club%20in%20April%202025.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67faba91a466d2b74ab3098e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223568%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGuests%20use%20payphones%20at%20the%20Masters%20at%20Augusta%20National%20Golf%20Club.%3Cp%3ERichard%20Heathcote%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAugusta%20National%20also%20allows%20patrons%20to%20bring%20cameras%20during%20the%20practice%20rounds%2C%20but%20they're%20prohibited%20on%20tournament%20days.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20neat%20to%20have%20a%20camera%20there%20to%20capture%20moments%2C%26quot%3B%20Wahlberg%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20got%20to%20get%20our%20selfies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20anti-cellphone%20wave%20has%20gained%20traction%20in%20recent%20years.%20Garth%20Brooks%20banned%20phones%20during%20his%20Las%20Vegas%20residency.%20Many%20comedians%20also%20now%20require%20guests%20to%20place%20their%20phones%20in%20cases%20until%20after%20the%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227303%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20patron%20at%20the%20Masters%20carries%20a%20disposable%20camera%20in%20April%202025.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67fabe6aa466d2b74ab309bc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224869%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPatrons%20can%20bring%20cameras%20to%20Augusta%20National%20Golf%20Club%20during%20the%20Masters'%20practice%20rounds.%3Cp%3EBen%20Jared%2FPGA%20TOUR%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20performers%20and%20athletes%2C%20however%2C%20still%20perform%20for%20a%20sea%20of%20cameras%20and%20smartphones.%20Wahlberg%20doesn't%20want%20that%20at%20the%20Masters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20patrons%20and%20fans%20of%20this%20event%20would%20appropriately%20riot%20if%20they%20ever%20decided%20to%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20Wahlberg%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20100%25%20hope%20we%20continue%20this%20trend%20of%20no%20cellphones%20at%20events.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFortunately%2C%20it%20doesn't%20appear%20Augusta%20National%20will%20change%20its%20policy%20anytime%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMasters%20chairman%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-masters-golf-tournament-bans-cell-phones%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFred%20Ridley%3C%2Fa%3E%20discussed%20the%20ban%20ahead%20of%20the%202019%20tournament%2C%20saying%20patrons%20appreciated%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20believe%20that's%20a%20policy%20that%20anyone%20should%20expect%20is%20going%20to%20change%20in%20the%20near%20future%2C%20if%20ever%2C%26quot%3B%20Ridley%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20can't%20speak%20for%20future%20chairmen%2C%20but%20speaking%20for%20myself%2C%20I%20think%20we%20got%20that%20right.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinside