%3Cp%3EUS%20Customs%20and%20Border%20Protection%20published%20the%20list%20of%20exemptions%20late%20Friday%20night.%20The%20guidance%20appears%20to%20exempt%20the%20products%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpresident-donald-trump-teases-exceptions-tariffs-baseline-levies-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrump's%20baseline%2010%25%20tariff%20rate%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20applies%20to%20most%20countries%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20145%25%20tariff%20specific%20to%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20welcome%20news%20to%20the%20tech%20industry.%20The%20exemptions%20came%20after%20a%20wild%20week%20in%20global%20financial%20markets.%20The%20intensifying%20trade%20war%20between%20the%20United%20States%20and%20China%20sowed%20chaos%20in%20both%20the%20stock%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbond-yields-sell-off-trump-tariffs-trade-war-us-debt-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebond%20markets%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20many%20tech%20giants%20have%20deep%20ties%20to%20China%2C%20Apple%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20is%20fully%20enmeshed%20in%20the%20country%2C%20where%20it%20has%20spent%20years%20building%20up%20the%20supply%20chain%20for%20its%20iPhones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20Wall%20Street%20analyst%20Dan%20Ives%20called%20the%20exemptions%20%26quot%3Bdream%20news%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUS%20Big%20Tech%20spoke%20and%20the%20White%20House%20made%20the%20right%20move%20at%20the%20right%20time.%20Massive%20relief%20for%20market%20and%20tech%20stocks%20into%20Sunday%20night%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Wedbush%20Securities%20managing%20director%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-venture-capitalists-investing-ai-machine-learning-startups-2022-10%23matt-turck-firstmark-capital-16%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETech%20investor%20Matt%20Turck%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20partner%20at%20the%20venture%20capital%20firm%20FirstMark%20Capital%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bexemptions%20come%20as%20a%20major%20relief%20to%20the%20tech%20and%20AI%20industry.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20%26quot%3Bthey're%20the%20sensical%20thing%20to%20do%20in%20an%20otherwise%20completely%20nonsensical%20series%20of%20decisions.%20This%20has%20been%20an%20embarrassing%20week%20for%20America.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tech%20industry%20might%20not%20be%20entirely%20in%20the%20clear%20just%20yet.%20The%20White%20House%20told%20BI%20in%20an%20email%20that%20Trump%20still%20intended%20to%20issue%20tariffs%20on%20certain%20tech%20products%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20plans%20to%20issue%20a%20section%20232%20study%2C%20an%20investigation%20into%20the%20impact%20of%20imports%20on%20national%20security%2C%20on%20semiconductors%2C%20which%20could%20determine%20whether%20the%20key%20technology%20is%20subject%20to%20tariffs%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPresident%20Trump%20has%20made%20it%20clear%20America%20cannot%20rely%20on%20China%20to%20manufacture%20critical%20technologies%20such%20as%20semiconductors%2C%20chips%2C%20smartphones%2C%20and%20laptops%2C%26quot%3B%20White%20House%20Press%20Secretary%20Karoline%20Leavitt%20told%20BI%20by%20email.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20why%20the%20President%20has%20secured%20trillions%20of%20dollars%20in%20US%20investments%20from%20the%20largest%20tech%20companies%20in%20the%20world%2C%20including%20Apple%2C%20TSMC%2C%20and%20Nvidia.%20At%20the%20direction%20of%20the%20President%2C%20these%20companies%20are%20hustling%20to%20onshore%20their%20manufacturing%20in%20the%20United%20States%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdream-news-tech-sector-trump-announces-tariff-exemptions-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744489464000%2