ed%20as%20violence%20erupted%20in%20Malda%2C%20Murshidabad%2C%20South%2024%20Parganas%20and%20Hooghly%20districts%20during%20protests%20over%20the%20new%20legislation%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20High%20Court%20underlined%20that%20every%20citizen%20has%20right%20to%20life%20and%20it%20is%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20state%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20life%20and%20property%20of%20every%20citizen%20is%20secured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConstitutional%20Courts%20cannot%20be%20a%20mute%20spectator%20and%20embroil%20itself%20in%20technical%20defences%20when%20the%20safety%20and%20security%20of%20the%20people%20are%20at%20danger.%20The%20deployment%20of%20Central%20Armed%20forces%20earlier%20could%20have%20escalated%20the%20situation%20as%20it%20appears%20adequate%20measures%20have%20not%20been%20taken%20in%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20noted%20that%20the%20situation%20is%20%26quot%3Bgrave%20and%20volatile%26quot%3B%2C%20underlining%20that%20action%20is%20to%20be%20taken%20against%20the%20culprits%20to%20arrest%20the%20atrocities%20committed%20on%20innocent%20citizens%20on%20%26quot%3Bwar%20footing%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20cannot%20turn%20a%20blind%20eye%20to%20the%20various%20reports%20that%20have%20surfaced%20which%20prima%20facie%20show%20vandalism%20in%20few%20districts%20of%20the%20state%20of%20West%20Bengal.%20The%20purpose%20of%20deployment%20of%20the%20para-military%20forces%20or%20Central%20Armed%20Police%20Force%20is%20only%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20facilitating%20the%20state%20administration%20to%20ensure%20the%20safety%20and%20security%20of%20the%20population%20in%20this%20State%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20court%2C%20adding%20it%20cannot%20be%20denied%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere%20is%20an%20internal%20disturbance%26quot%3B%20in%20some%20of%20the%20districts%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20central%20forces%20will%20operate%20in%20coordination%20with%20the%20state%20administration.%20The%20court%20also%20instructed%20both%20the%20state%20government%20and%20the%20Centre%20to%20submit%20detailed%20reports%20on%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20special%20bench%20comprising%20Justices%20Soumen%20Sen%20and%20Raja%20Basu%20Chowdhury%20was%20constituted%20by%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20to%20urgently%20hear%20a%20petition%20filed%20by%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%2C%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20West%20Bengal%20Assembly%2C%20seeking%20the%20deployment%20of%20central%20forces%20in%20the%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20matter%20is%20scheduled%20for%20further%20hearing%20on%20April%2017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovernor%20CV%20Ananda%20Bose%20on%20Saturday%20night%20welcomed%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court's%20directive%20for%20the%20deployment%20of%20central%20forces%20in%20violence-hit%20areas%20of%20Murshidabad%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20been%20told%20about%20the%20deployment%20of%20CAPF%20in%20the%20riot-affected%20areas%20of%20Bengal%2C%20including%20Murshidabad.%20I%20am%20glad%20that%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20stepped%20in%20and%20given%20the%20appropriate%20decision%20in%20appropriate%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Governor%20said%20in%20a%20video%20message%20released%20by%20Raj%20Bhavan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20declared%20that%20her%20state%20would%20not%20implement%20the%20controversial%20Waqf%20(Amendment)%20Act%20and%20appealed%20for%20peace%20and%20harmony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20made%20our%20position%20clear%20on%20this%20matter%20-%20we%20do%20not%20support%20this%20law.%20This%20law%20will%20not%20be%20implemented%20in%20our%20state.%20So%20what%20is%20the%20riot%20about%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Banerjee%20cautioned%20against%20political%20misuse%20of%20religion%20and%20warned%20of%20legal%20action%20against%20those%20inciting%20riots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRemember%2C%20we%20did%20not%20make%20the%20law%20that%20many%20are%20agitating%20against.%20The%20law%20was%20made%20by%20the%20central%20government.%20So%20the%20answer%20you%20want%20should%20be%20sought%20from%20the%20central%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDirector%20General%20of%20Police%20Rajeev%20Kumar%20cautioned%20the%20agitators%20that%20the%20state%20police%20will%20not%20tolerate%20any%20attempts%20to%20disrupt%20law%20and%20order%20in%20the%20name%20of%20the%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744482060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2F40otcrs4_bengal-violence-_625x300_12_April_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fappears-measures-not-taken-in-time-calcutta-high-court-on-bengal-waqf-violence-8150519%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Underlining%20that%20constitutional%20courts%20cannot%20be%20a%20mute%20spectator%2C%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20on%20Saturday%20ordered%20the%20deployment%20of%20Central%20forces%20in%20Bengal's%20Murshidabad%20where%20anti-Waqf%20protests%20have%20resulted%20in%20the%20death%20of%20three%20people.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IPL%202025%3A%20Abhishek%20Scripts%20Mammoth%20Record%20As%20SRH%20Rout%20PBKS%20By%208%20Wickets%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESunrisers%20Hyderabad%20vs%20Punjab%20Kings%20Highlights%2C%20IPL%202025%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Abhishek%20Sharma%20played%20a%20record%20knock%20as%20Sunrisers%20Hyderabad%20registered%20an%20easy%20eight-wicket%20win%20over%20Punjab%20Kings%20in%20their%20IPL%202025%20match%20in%20Hyderabad%20on%20Saturday.%20Abhishek%20scored%20141%20runs%20off%2055%20balls%20with%20the%20help%20of%2014%20fours%20and%2010%20sixes%2C%20becoming%20the%20Indian%20player%20with%20the%20highest%20individual%20score%20i