Don't%20Play%20Victim%26quot%3B%3A%20UK-Based%20Gangster%20Says%20He%20Gave%20Hit%20Order%20On%20Delhi%20Man%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20gangster%20living%20in%20London%20has%20taken%20responsibility%20for%20the%20killing%20of%20a%2052-year-old%20property%20dealer%20in%20Delhi.%20Rajkumar%20Dalal%20was%20driving%20his%20Toyota%20Fortuner%20when%20two%20cars%20approached%20from%20the%20side%20and%20opened%20fire%20at%20outer%20Delhi's%20Paschim%20Vihar%20(East)%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police's%20suspicion%20of%20a%20gang%20war%20behind%20the%20killing%20came%20true%20when%20the%20London-based%20gangster%2C%20Kapil%20Sangwan%20alias%20Nandu%2C%20in%20a%20post%20on%20Facebook%20said%20he%20gave%20the%20hit%20order%20on%20the%20property%20dealer%20because%20he%20was%20doing%20the%20bidding%20of%20Manjeet%20Mahal%2C%20a%20Delhi-based%20gangster.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20got%20the%20murder%20done.%20He%20used%20to%20occupy%20a%20plot%20for%20my%20enemy%20Manjeet%20Mahal.%20When%20out%20on%20parole%2C%20I%20met%20Manjeet%20Mahal%20and%20told%20him%20that%20whoever%20supports%20him%20would%20become%20my%20enemy%2C%26quot%3B%20Nandu%20said%20in%20the%20post%20written%20in%20Hindi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDon't%20play%20this%20victim%20card.%20You%20started%20it.%20I%20am%20going%20to%20finish%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Nandu%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENandu%2C%20who%20is%20hiding%20in%20London%2C%20faces%20an%20Interpol%20Red%20Corner%20Notice%20(RCN).%20Interpol%20issues%20an%20RCN%20at%20the%20request%20of%20a%20member%20country%20to%20seek%20the%20location%20and%20arrest%20of%20wanted%20people%20globally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20police%20officer%20said%20the%20case%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20transferred%20to%20the%20Delhi%20Police's%20Crime%20Branch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20killers%20fired%20some%2015%20rounds%20at%20the%20property%20dealer.%20It%20is%20suspected%20they%20scanned%20the%20area%20and%20observed%20the%20target%20before%20striking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajkumar%20Dalal%20was%20going%20from%20Paschim%20Vihar%20to%20his%20gym%20in%20Punjabi%20Bagh%20when%20the%20attack%20happened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20checking%20CCTV%20camera%20footage%20from%20the%20crime%20scene%20to%20identify%20the%20attackers.%20A%20case%20has%20been%20registered%20and%20multiple%20teams%20have%20been%20formed%20to%20crack%20the%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20police%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20property%20dealer%20is%20survived%20by%20his%20wife%20Sujata%2C%20and%20their%20son%2C%20who%20is%20a%20doctor.%20Police%20sources%20said%20Rajkumar%20Dalal's%20family%20were%20not%20aware%20of%20any%20enmity%20that%20he%20may%20have%20had.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744481160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Fmaltgol_kapil-sangwan_625x300_03_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdont-play-victim-card-london-based-gangster-kapil-sangwan-says-he-gave-hit-order-on-delhi-property-dealer-8150518%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20gangster%20living%20in%20London%20has%20taken%20responsibility%20for%20the%20killing%20of%20a%2052-year-old%20property%20dealer%20in%20Delhi.%20Rajkumar%20Dalal%20was%20driving%20his%20Toyota%20Fortuner%20when%20two%20cars%20approached%20from%20the%20side%20and%20opened%20fire%20at%20outer%20Delhi's%20Paschim%20Vihar.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rajesh%20had%20mixed%20thoughts%20about%20playing%20SRK's%20boss%20in%20Don%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744480332000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-120238779%2Cimgsize-30180.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Frajesh-khattar-reveals-he-had-mixed-thoughts-about-playing-shah-rukh-khans-boss-in-farhan-akhtars-d