20Russian%20missile%20struck%20the%20warehouse%20of%20an%20Indian%20pharmaceutical%20company%20in%20Kyiv%2C%20Ukraine%20said%20today.%20The%20country's%20embassy%20in%20India%20alleged%20Russia%20%26quot%3Bdeliberately%26quot%3B%20targeted%20Indian%20businesses%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20a%20Russian%20missile%20struck%20the%20warehouse%20of%20Indian%20pharmaceutical%20company%20Kusum%20in%20Ukraine.%20While%20claiming%20'special%20friendship'%20with%20India%2C%20Moscow%20deliberately%20targets%20Indian%20businesses%20-%20destroying%20medicines%20meant%20for%20children%20and%20the%20elderly%2C%26quot%3B%20Ukraine's%20embassy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKusum%2C%20owned%20by%20Indian%20businessman%20Rajiv%20Gupta%2C%20is%20among%20the%20largest%20pharma%20firms%20in%20Ukraine.%20The%20company's%20products%20are%20critical%20across%20Ukraine%20as%20they%20ensure%20availability%20of%20basic%20medicines%2C%20sources%20told%20NDTV.%20They%20said%20a%20drone%2C%20not%20a%20missile%2C%20made%20a%20direct%20hit%20on%20the%20warehouse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20Kyiv's%20post%2C%20Britain's%20ambassador%20to%20Ukraine%20Martin%20Harris%20said%20Russian%20strikes%20destroyed%20a%20major%20pharma's%20warehouse%20in%20Kyiv.%20Mr%20Martin%2C%20however%2C%20also%20said%20the%20attack%20was%20carried%20out%20by%20Russian%20drones%2C%20not%20a%20missile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20morning%20Russian%20drones%20completely%20destroyed%20a%20major%20pharmaceuticals%20warehouse%20in%20Kyiv%2C%20incinerating%20stocks%20of%20medicines%20needed%20by%20the%20elderly%20and%20children.%20Russia's%20campaign%20of%20terror%20against%20Ukrainian%20civilians%20continues%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Martin%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EToday%2C%20a%20Russian%20missile%20struck%20the%20warehouse%20of%20Indian%20pharmaceutical%20company%20Kusum%20in%20Ukraine.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnWhile%20claiming%20%26quot%3Bspecial%20friendship%26quot%3B%20with%20India%2C%20Moscow%20deliberately%20targets%20Indian%20businesses%20-%20destroying%20medicines%20meant%20for%20children%20and%20the%20elderly.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FrussiaIsATerroristState%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23russiaIsATerroristState%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FAW2JMKulst%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FAW2JMKulst%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20UKR%20Embassy%20in%20India%20(%40UkrembInd)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUkrembInd%2Fstatus%2F1911083540390756663%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%2012%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20British%20envoy%20to%20Ukraine%20posted%20a%20photo%20showing%20smoke%20rising%20from%20a%20structure%20that%20appeared%20to%20be%20a%20warehouse%2C%20along%20with%20a%20fire%20engine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20Russia's%20defence%20ministry%20alleged%20Ukraine%20carried%20out%20five%20attacks%20on%20Russian%20energy%20infrastructure%20over%20the%20past%20day%2C%20a%20violation%20of%20a%20US-brokered%20moratorium%20on%20such%20strikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUkraine%20and%20Russia%20agreed%20to%20pause%20strikes%20on%20each%20other's%20energy%20facilities%20last%20month%2C%20but%20both%20sides%20have%20repeatedly%20accused%20each%20other%20of%20breaking%20the%20moratorium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20India%20has%20called%20for%20peace%20and%20an%20end%20to%20violence%20between%20Ukraine%20and%20Russia%2C%20it%20has%20not%20openly%20taken%20sides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20been%20buying%20a%20large%20volume%20of%20oil%20from%20Russia%20soon%20after%20the%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%20in%20February%202022.%20This%20is%20primarily%20because%20Russian%20oil%20was%20available%20at%20a%20significant%20discount%20to%20other%20international%20benchmarks%20due%20to%20Western%20sanctions%20and