wn%20on%20illegal%20immigration%20and%20deport%20millions%20living%20illegally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Alien%20Registration%20Requirement%20(ARR)%20originates%20from%20the%20Alien%20Registration%20Act%20of%201940.%20This%20particular%20law%20also%20required%20immigrants%20in%20the%20US%20to%20register%2C%20but%20it%20was%20never%20consistently%20implemented.%20However%2C%20the%20new%20rules%20will%20ensure%20the%20strict%20implementation%20of%20the%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EWH%20Press%20Secretary%2C%20Karoline%20Leavitt%3A%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnALL%20Illegal%20Aliens%20present%20in%20the%20United%20States%20longer%20than%2030%20days%20must%20register%20with%20the%20federal%20government%E2%80%A6%20If%20not%2C%20you%20will%20be%20arrested%2C%20fined%2C%20deported%2C%20never%20to%20return%20to%20our%20country%20again.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FA0h2lOB3TA%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FA0h2lOB3TA%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FwAkkbRdafd%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FwAkkbRdafd%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20XRP%20NESARA-GESARA%20QFS%203.0%20(%40NesaraGesara0)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNesaraGesara0%2Fstatus%2F1910848438423507192%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%2012%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EKey%20Provisions%20of%20the%20Rule%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20Mandatory%20Registration%3A%20All%20non-citizens%20above%2014%20years%20old%20staying%20in%20the%20US%20for%2030%20days%20or%20more%20must%20register%20with%20the%20government%20using%20%26quot%3BForm%20G-325R%26quot%3B.%20Parents%20will%20need%20to%20register%20for%20their%20children%20under%2014.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn-%20Documentation%20Requirements%3A%20Those%20arriving%20in%20the%20US%20on%20or%20after%20April%2011%20must%20register%20within%2030%20days%20of%20arrival.%20Failure%20to%20comply%20may%20result%