egde%20commission%20recommended%20a%20reclassification%20based%20on%20occupation%20and%20social%20condition.%20Some%20castes%20currently%20in%20Category%201%20will%20be%20moved%20to%20Category%201A%20based%20on%20occupational%20criteria.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECertain%20communities%20from%20Category%201%20and%202A%20will%20be%20reclassified%20into%20Category%201B%20based%20on%20the%20current%20social%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20categorisation%20is%20based%20on%20skills%2C%20nomadic%20lifestyle%2C%20and%20traditional%20occupation%20such%20as%20artisan%20and%20caste-based%20professions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20caste-wise%20population%20data%20from%20the%20census%20report%20is%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETotal%20population%20covered%20in%20the%20caste%20survey%3A%205%2C98%2C14%2C942%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESC%20population%3A%201%2C09%2C29%2C347%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EST%20population%3A%2042%2C81%2C289%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECategory%201A%3A%2034%2C96%2C638%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECategory%201B%3A%2073%2C92%2C313%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECategory%202A%3A%2077%2C78%2C209%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECategory%202B%3A%2075%2C25%2C880%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECategory%203A%3A%2072%2C99%2C577%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECategory%203B%3A%2081%2C37%2C536%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20was%20submitted%20to%20the%20state%20cabinet%20in%20more%20than%2046%20volumes.%20Data%20on%20various%20aspects%20of%20the%20caste%20survey%20was%20recorded%20in%20two%20CDs%20and%20given%20to%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20during%20his%20first%20tenure%20as%20chief%20minister%2C%20Siddaramaiah%20ordered%20the%20Karnataka%20Socio-Economic%20and%20Educational%20Census.%20A%20committee%20headed%20by%20the%20then%20Backward%20Classes%20Commission%20Chairman%20H%20Kantharaju%20did%20the%20survey%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20around%20Rs%20169%20crore.%20The%20report%20was%20ready%20by%202016%3B%20it%20was%2C%20however%2C%20put%20in%20cold%20storage%20by%20subsequent%20governments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20and%20Janata%20Dal%20(Secular)%20coalition%20government%20headed%20by%20HD%20Kumaraswamy%20and%20the%20BJP%20government%20headed%20by%20BS%20Yediyurappa%20and%20Basavaraj%20Bommai%20also%20kept%20the%20report%20pending.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20parties%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20JD(S)%20have%20opposed%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20report.%20Major%20caste%20groups%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Lingayats%20and%20Vokkaligas%2C%20alleged%20the%20report%20has%20done%20injustice%20to%20them%20in%20terms%20of%20their%20population%20representation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeader%20of%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Karnataka%20assembly%20R%20Ashoka%20said%20on%20Friday%20the%20caste%20census%20report%20prepared%20by%20the%20Siddaramaiah%20government%20was%20not%20scientific.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20people%20conducting%20the%20caste%20census%20did%20not%20visit%20every%20household.%20This%20report%20was%20prepared%20under%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah's%20instructions.%20Since%20it%20has%20political%20motives%2C%20no%20one%20will%20accept%20it.%20I%2C%20too%2C%20am%20saying%20that%20a%20caste%20census%20should%20be%20conducted.%20But%20this%20report%20was%20designed%20to%20sow%20discord%20among%20castes%20for%20someone's%20benefit%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Ashoka%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiddaramaiah%20in%20February%20said%20the%20caste%20census%20was%20conducted%20scientifically%20and%20his%20government%20would%20implement%20it%20without%20any%20doubt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20government%20supports%20the%20caste%20census.%20We%20have%20accepted%20the%20caste%20census%20report%20and%20will%20certainly%20implement%20it%20in%20the%20coming%20days.%20There%20is%20no%20need%20for%20any%20doubt%20regarding%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744473060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F6fokp3u8_caste-census-generic_625x300_23_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3