-For-1%20Deal%2C%20Alliance%20With%20AIADMK%20Also%20Strengthens%20BJP%20In%20Rajya%20Sabha%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20renewed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faiadmk-bjp-to-fight-tamil-nadu-polls-together-next-year-under-leadership-of-edapaddi-k-palaniswami-says-amit-shah-8140726%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBJP-AIADMK%20alliance%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%3C%2Fa%3E%20-%20announced%20Friday%20evening%20by%20Home%20Minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Famit-shah%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmit%20Shah%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20ex-Chief%20Minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fedappadi-k-palaniswami%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEdappadi%20K%20Palaniswami%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20his%20side%20-%20gives%20the%20former%20a%20premade%20political%20platform%2C%20i.e.%2C%20access%20to%20an%20established%20cadre%20and%20voter%20base%20before%20next%20year's%20state%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20effective%20that%20platform%20will%20be%20-%20given%20the%20margin%20of%20victory%20the%20ruling%20DMK-Congress%20alliance%20enjoyed%20in%20the%202021%20Assembly%20and%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20-%20is%20not%20clear%2C%20particularly%20since%20the%20BJP%20has%20historically%20struggled%20in%20a%20state%20that%20rejects%20its%20muscular%20brand%20of%20nationalism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20and%20perhaps%20more%20crucially%2C%20it%20also%20gives%20the%20BJP%20a%20boost%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20because%20it%20can%20now%20count%20on%20the%20AIADMK's%20four%20MPs%20and%20this%20gives%20it%20a%20mathematical%20edge%20in%20the%20Upper%20House%20and%2C%20by%20extension%2C%20a%20stranglehold%20on%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP-led%20coalition%20already%20enjoys%20a%20brute%20majority%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20is%20now%20set%20to%20control%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20too%2C%20meaning%20the%20passage%20of%20bills%20-%20particularly%20controversial%20ones%20like%20the%20'one%20nation%2C%20one%20election'%20bill%20expected%20in%20the%20next%20Parliament%20session%20-%20should%20be%20much%20easier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20sources%20have%20told%20NDTV%20pushing%20the%20'one%20nation%2C%20one%20election'%20bill%20-%20a%20flagship%20initiative%20of%20PM%20Modi%20-%20through%20Parliament%20is%20the%20priority%2C%20after%20changes%20to%20the%20Waqf%20laws%20were%20cleared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP's%20Rajya%20Sabha%20Majority%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rajya%20Sabha%20has%20a%20total%20strength%20of%20245%2C%20of%20which%20nine%20seats%20are%20vacant.%20This%20means%20the%20effective%20strength%20is%20only%20236%20and%20the%20majority%20mark%20is%20119%2C%20which%20the%20BJP%20can%20now%20clear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20addition%20of%20four%20current%20AIADMK%20MPs%20-%20CV%20Shanmugam%2C%20M%20Thambidurai%2C%20N%20Chandrasegharan%2C%20and%C2%A0%20R%20Dharmar%20-%20the%20BJP-led%20ruling%20alliance%20will%20have%20123%20MPs%20on%20its%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20could%20go%20to%20124%20because%20the%20term%20of%20Anbumani%20Ramadoss%20of%20the%20PMK%2C%20a%20regional%20Tamil%20party%2C%20ends%20in%20July.%20And%2C%20based%20on%20the%20current%20make-up%20of%20the%20Assembly%2C%20the%20AIADMK%20should%20be%20able%20to%20pick%20up%20this%20seat%20too%2C%20taking%20its%20tally%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20to%20five.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20BJP%20can%20also%20count%20on%20support%20from%20seven%20other%20MPs%20-%20six%20nominated%20and%20one%20independent.%20The%20party-led%20NDA's%20effective%20strength%2C%20therefore%2C%20is%20131.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ENumbers%20Could%20Go%20Up%20More%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20one%20seat%20vacant%20from%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20which%20was%20held%20by%20ex-Chief%20Minister%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy's%20YSR%20Congress%20Party.%20That%20will%20now%20go%20to%20the%20ruling%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20of%20Chief%20Minister%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%2C%20who%20is%20a%20key%20ally%2C%20and%20therefore%20to%20the%20NDA's%20side%20of%20the%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20there%20are%20four%20seats%20vacant%20for%20nominated%20MPs%20and%20the%20picks%20for%20these%20seats%20will%20almost%20certainly%20side%20with%20the%20BJP.%20And%20then%20there%20are%20four%20vacant%20from%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElections%20for%20those%20seats%20have%20been%20delayed%20but%2C%20when%20held%2C%20the%20BJP%20will%20expect%20to%20pick%20up%20at%20least%20one%20seat%20given%2029%20MLAs%20in%20the%2090-seat%20House.%20Mr%20Modi's%20party%20may%20even%20get%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20this%20means%20the%20BJP%20could%20count%20on%20as%20many%20as%20141%20seats%20in%20the%20245-member%20House%20and%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%202014%2C%20the%20party-led%20alliance%20could%20enjoy%20a%20clear%20majority%20in%20the%20Upper%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20added%20emphasis%20the%20BJP%20can%20also%20count%20on%20issue-based%20votes%20from%20non-aligned%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20to%20clear%20the%20Waqf%20(Amendment)%20Bill%20through%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20the%20BJP%20could%20count%20on%20individual%20votes%20from%20Odisha's%20BJD%20and%20the%20YSR%20Congress%20Party%2C%20each%20of%20which%20has%20seven%20MPs%20and%20neither%20of%20which%20issued%20a%20whip%20directing%20its%20members%20to%20vote%20in%20a%20particular%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744469880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fis3srf9_rajya-sabha-_625x300_04_April_25.jpg