-haryana-student-caught-entering-boys-hostel-8148141%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20student%20of%20a%20private%20university%20in%20Haryana%20has%20become%20the%20centre%20of%20an%20unusual%20controversy%20after%20being%20caught%20attempting%20to%20smuggle%20a%20girl%2C%20believed%20to%20be%20his%20girlfriend%2C%20into%20the%20university's%20boys'%20hostel.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgirlfriend-in-suitcase-haryana-student-caught-entering-boys-hostel-8148141%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ukraine%20Could%20Resemble%20Postwar%20Berlin%2C%20With%20Allied%20Zones%20Of%20Control%3A%20US%20Envoy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20special%20envoy%20to%20Ukraine%2C%20General%20Keith%20Kellogg%2C%20has%20proposed%20a%20potential%20solution%20to%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%20between%20Ukraine%20and%20Russia.%20According%20to%20Kellogg%2C%20Ukraine%20could%20be%20divided%20into%20zones%20of%20control%2C%20similar%20to%20post-World%20War%20II%20Berlin%2C%20per%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thetimes.com%2Fus%2Famerican-politics%2Farticle%2Fkeith-kellogg-general-ukraine-envoy-trump-ldjprpzxt%3Ft%3D1744441838476%5C%22%3EThe%20Times%20Of%20London%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20suggested%20that%20British%20and%20French%20troops%20could%20serve%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Breassurance%20force%26quot%3B%20in%20western%20Ukraine%2C%20while%20Russian%20forces%20maintain%20control%20over%20the%20eastern%20regions%20they've%20occupied.%20A%20demilitarised%20zone%20and%20Ukrainian%20troops%20would%20separate%20the%20two%20forces.%20Kellogg%20drew%20parallels%20between%20his%20proposal%20and%20the%20division%20of%20Berlin%20after%20World%20War%20II%2C%20stating%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20could%20almost%20make%20it%20look%20like%20what%20happened%20with%20Berlin%20after%20World%20War%20Two%2C%20when%20you%20had%20a%20Russian%20zone%2C%20a%20French%20zone%2C%20and%20a%20British%20zone%2C%20a%20US%20zone.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnHowever%2C%20Kellogg%20later%20clarified%20on%20social%20media%20that%20his%20comments%20were%20misrepresented%2C%20emphasising%20that%20he%20was%20discussing%20a%20post-ceasefire%20resiliency%20force%20supporting%20Ukraine's%20sovereignty%2C%20not%20partitioning%20the%20country.%20He%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20speaking%20of%20a%20post-ceasefire%20resiliency%20force%20in%20support%20of%20Ukraine's%20sovereignty.%20In%20discussions%20of%20partitioning%2C%20I%20was%20referencing%20areas%20or%20zones%20of%20responsibility%20for%20an%20allied%20force%20(without%20U.S.%20troops).%20I%20was%20NOT%20referring%20to%20a%20partitioning%20of%20Ukraine.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20Times%20article%20misrepresents%20what%20I%20said.%20I%20was%20speaking%20of%20a%20post-cease%20fire%20resiliency%20force%20in%20support%20of%20Ukraine's%20sovereignty.%20In%20discussions%20of%20partitioning%2C%20I%20was%20referencing%20areas%20or%20zones%20of%20responsibility%20for%20an%20allied%20force%20(without%20US%20troops).%20I%20was%20NOT%20referring%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FwFBcEVjxtO%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FwFBcEVjxtO%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Keith%20Kellogg%20(%40generalkellogg)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgeneralkellogg%2Fstatus%2F1910811346251268305%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%2011%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky%20has%20firmly%20rejected%20any%20territorial%20concessions%20to%20Russia%20and%20Ukraine%20has%20consistently%20refused%20to%20consider%20ceasefire%20or%20peace%20deals%20involving%20land%20cessions%2C%20Defense%20Secretary%20Pete%20Hegseth%20has%20called%20it%20%26quot%3Bunrealistic%26quot%3B%20to%20expect%20a%20return%20to%20Ukraine's%20pre-2014%20borders.%20Russia's%20Foreign%20Minister%20Sergey%20Lavrov%20has%20also%20stated%20that%20the%20Kremlin%20would%20not%20accept%20peacekeeping%20troops%20from%20any%20NATO%20country%20under%20any%20circumstances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20another%20US%20special%20envoy%2C%20Steve%20Witkoff%2C%20held%20a%20four-hour%20meeting%20with%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20in%20St.%20Petersburg%2C%20urged%20by%20President%20Trump%20to%20%26quot%3Bget%20moving%26quot%3B%20on%20a%20ceasefire.%20Despite%20Zelensky's%20repeated%20insistence%20on%20Ukraine's%20involvement%20in%20talks%2C%20no%20Ukrainian%20representatives%20were%20present%20at%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20on%20the%20ground%20remains%20dire%2C%20with%20Russia%20launching%20a%20large-scale%20drone%20attack%20across%20Ukraine%20on%20Friday%20night%2C%20resulting%20in%20injuries%20and%20damage.%20Ukrainian%20officials%20reported%20that%2056%20out%20of%2088%20drones%20were%20shot%20down%2C%20while%2024%20more%20were%20redirected%20using%20electronic%20warfare.%20Kyiv%20mayor%20Vitali%20Klitchko%20said%20that%20three%20people%20were%20injured%20in%20the%20capital%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20drone%20attacks%2C%20and%20one%20more%20person%20was%20wounded%20in%20the%20city%20of%20Kharkiv%20in%20the%20northeast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20context%2C%20Kellogg's%20proposal%20takes%20on%20significant%20importance.%20The%20potential%20use%20of%20the%20Dnipro%20river%20as%20a%20demarcation%20line%20within%20Ukraine%20after%20a%20ceasefire%20is%20a%20key%20aspect%20of%20the%20proposal.%20However%2C%20the%20details%20and%20implications%20of%20this%20idea%20are%20still%20unclear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20support%20for%20fresh%20elections%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20as%20mentioned%20by%20Kellogg%2C%20is%20also%20noteworthy.%20This%20move%20could%20be%20seen%20as%20an%20attempt%20to%20bring%20Putin%20back%20to%20the%20ne