0are%20deployed%20near%20the%20lake%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20task%20from%20April%20to%20December%2C%20before%20the%20lake%20starts%20freezing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20weeds%20are%20first%20weighed%20to%20maintain%20proper%20records%20before%20being%20unloaded%20in%20a%20designated%20area%20for%20processing%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20social%20entrepreneur%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20weeds%20are%20first%20dried%20in%20a%20dewatering%20plant%20to%20remove%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F288849%2Feasy-monsoon-hacks-to-protect-your-home-from-damp-smell-moisture%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eas%20much%20moisture%20as%20possible%3C%2Fa%3E.%20After%20that%2C%20they%20go%20through%20a%20two-step%20shredding%20process%20that%20breaks%20them%20down%20into%20small%20pieces%2C%20each%20less%20than%204%20mm%20in%20size.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20produce%20higher-quality%20manure%20when%20it%20is%20finely%20shredded%2C%E2%80%9D%20Maninder%20explains.%20The%20shredded%20material%20is%20then%20placed%20in%20windrows%20(3m%20wide%2C%2090m%20long)%20for%20controlled%20composting%20over%20two%20to%20three%20weeks.%20Afterward%2C%20it%20is%20sun-dried%20to%20further%20reduce%20moisture.%20Bio-nutrients%20and%20organic%20enhancers%20are%20added%20to%20improve%20the%20manure%E2%80%99s%20NPK%20(Nitrogen%2C%20Phosphorus%2C%20and%20Potassium)%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20composting%20process%2C%20the%20material%20is%20screened%2C%20refined%20into%20a%20powdered%20form%2C%20and%20packed%20in%20bags%20of%20various%20sizes%20for%20distribution.%20The%20entire%20process%20takes%20about%2035%E2%80%9340%20days%20from%20arrival%20to%20packaging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20people%20behind%20the%20progress%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20distribution%20network%20is%20one%20of%20the%20main%20reasons%20behind%20our%20success%2C%20a